---
const { site = {}, compact = false } = Astro.props;
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const links = site.legalLinks || {
  privacy: '/privacy',
  terms: '/terms',
  emailPolicy: '/email-policy',
  legalNotice: '/legal-notice'
};
---

<footer class:list={["yb-legal-footer", { "yb-legal-footer--compact": compact }]}>
  <div class="yb-legal-footer__inner">
    <div class="yb-legal-footer__head">
      <div>
        <p class="yb-legal-footer__title">
          <strong>{site.operatorName || '법무법인 윤빛'}</strong>
          <span aria-hidden="true">|</span>
          <b>{site.shortName || '금융사기 피해회복센터'}</b>
        </p>
        <p class="yb-legal-footer__sub">금융사기 피해 정황 안내 및 법률상담 접수</p>
      </div>

      <nav class="yb-legal-footer__links" aria-label="법적 고지">
        <a href={links.privacy}>개인정보처리방침</a>
        <a href={links.terms}>이용약관</a>
        <a href={links.emailPolicy}>이메일무단수집거부</a>
        <a href={links.legalNotice}>면책·광고 고지</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="yb-legal-footer__business" aria-label="사업자 정보">
      <p><strong>운영 주체</strong><span>{site.operatorName || '법무법인 윤빛'}</span></p>
      <p><strong>광고책임변호사</strong><span>{site.responsibleAttorney || '윤수빈 변호사'}</span></p>
      <p><strong>사업자등록번호</strong><span>{site.businessNumber || '754-87-03255'}</span></p>
      <p class="wide"><strong>주소</strong><span>{site.address || '서울특별시 강남구 영동대로 621, 621빌딩 11층'}</span></p>
      <p><strong>대표전화</strong><a href={site.telLink || 'tel:01021754252'}>{site.phone || '010-2175-4252'}</a></p>
      <p><strong>이메일</strong><a href={`mailto:${site.email || 'contact@yoonbitlawfirm.com'}`}>{site.email || 'contact@yoonbitlawfirm.com'}</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="yb-legal-footer__notice">
      <p>본 웹사이트의 내용은 일반적인 피해 정황 및 절차 안내이며, 개별 사건에 대한 구체적인 법률의견이나 결과 보장을 의미하지 않습니다.</p>
      <p>상담 내용과 사건 결과는 사실관계, 증거자료, 상대방 특정 여부 및 관계기관의 판단에 따라 달라질 수 있습니다.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="yb-legal-footer__copy">© {year} {site.operatorName || '법무법인 윤빛'}. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .yb-legal-footer {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015), transparent 44%),
      var(--yb-bg-deep);
    color: var(--yb-text);
    padding: 54px 22px 58px;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__inner {
    width: min(1120px, 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 32px;
    padding-bottom: 27px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__title {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.35;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__title strong {
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__title span {
    color: var(--yb-accent-2);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__title b {
    font-weight: 620;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__sub {
    margin: 8px 0 0;
    color: var(--yb-muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    gap: 8px 18px;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__links a {
    position: relative;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.70);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__links a:hover,
  .yb-legal-footer__links a:focus-visible {
    color: var(--yb-accent-2);
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__links a:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--yb-accent-2);
    outline-offset: 4px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__business {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 10px 28px;
    padding: 27px 0 22px;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__business p {
    min-width: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__business p.wide {
    grid-column: span 2;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__business strong {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__business span,
  .yb-legal-footer__business a {
    min-width: 0;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__business a:hover,
  .yb-legal-footer__business a:focus-visible {
    color: var(--yb-accent-2);
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__notice {
    display: grid;
    gap: 4px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__notice p,
  .yb-legal-footer__copy {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.43);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer__copy {
    margin-top: 19px;
  }

  .yb-legal-footer--compact {
    padding-top: 42px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .yb-legal-footer__head {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .yb-legal-footer__links {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .yb-legal-footer__business {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 580px) {
    .yb-legal-footer {
      padding: 40px 18px 44px;
    }

    .yb-legal-footer__head {
      padding-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .yb-legal-footer__title {
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .yb-legal-footer__links {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      width: 100%;
      gap: 10px 16px;
    }

    .yb-legal-footer__links a {
      font-size: 12.5px;
    }

    .yb-legal-footer__business {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 23px 0 19px;
    }

    .yb-legal-footer__business p.wide {
      grid-column: auto;
    }

    .yb-legal-footer__business p {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 104px minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
  }
</style>
